Package: gitr
Title: A Lightweight API for Git
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stu", "Field", email = "stu.g.field@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")) 
    )
Description: A light-weight, dependency-free, API to access
    system-level git commands from within R. Contains wrappers
    and defaults for common data science workflows as well as
    Z-shell plugin aliases. Generalized API syntax is also available.
    A system installation of git is required.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.io/gitr/
BugReports: https://github.com/stufield/gitr/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    spelling,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    withr
VignetteBuilder:
    knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
